{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"**Bug**: The `handleAPIStepContent` handler passed the raw DSL config value (e.g., `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")`) directly to `os.ReadFile` instead of extracting the inner path first. This caused every file read to fail silently, resulting in the drawer showing the filename but never loading the content.","timestamp":"2026-03-09T15:31:25.339357778Z"}
